{"tid":552922,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(賞櫻行程) 名古屋入大阪走三重遊","createTime":"2018-02-07T03:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T06:28:32.000Z","uid":97710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c077fee19b323ea77847906e1edec0efd3990c7","tid":552922,"uid":97710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"黎緊4月頭會去名古屋+三重+大阪自駕<br />\n上網搵都好少關於三重縣既行程<br />\n求大家狠批 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 (住名古屋站)  7點中部機場落機 -&gt; 名古屋站<br />\nDay 2 (住名古屋站) 鶴舞公園睇櫻花(希望仲睇到) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -&gt; 荒子川公園 (都係睇櫻花) -&gt; 港水族館<br />\nDay 3 (住湯之山) 早上出車 -&gt; 長島outlet (順便去埋麵包超人館) -&gt; 去酒店摘士多啤梨  -&gt; 一泊兩食<br />\nDay 4 (住伊勢) 去松阪沿途經過去下d公園睇櫻花 (應該少人d) -&gt; 午餐食一升 -&gt; 去宮川堤睇櫻花 -&gt; 夫婦岩+水族館 -&gt; 一泊兩食<br />\nDay 5 (住津) 早上去內宮+おかげ横丁 -&gt; 午餐海女小屋 -&gt; 鳥羽水族館 (又係水族館 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nDay 6 (住大阪天王寺) 伊賀上野城 -&gt; 忍者屋 -&gt; 奈良又睇下櫻花 -&gt; 大阪還車<br />\nDay 7 (住大阪天王寺) 大阪shopping<br />\nDay 8 中午機關西回港<br />\n<br />\n好似去得好多水族館但係又真係唔知可以去邊<br />\n有無人可能提議下Day 5 下午 同埋 Day 6 有無野好做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7150194d6a06154d880916aada3b385c29c3d8f","tid":552922,"uid":97710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通真係無乜人去三重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344a2cb659dbaeea404ba3da0923f73265993454","tid":552922,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"建議可以坐上近鐵特急架車. 可以由鳥羽返返去大阪難波.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kintetsu.co.jp/foreign/chinese-han/shimak